snippet.title: Kingdom Under Fire II - 2010 G Star Trailer
snippet.description: This trailer revealed at 2010 G Star features MMO elements of the game along with mind blowing action that will put you on the edge of your seat!  Also we're happy to let you know that KUF2 was one of the top five most popular games at the show!
